<cb:div type="nanchuan-notes">
<head>漢譯南傳大藏經 註解</head>
<p>
<note n="0101001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0101001">讀為 Bhūtasabbāni（異本）。</note>
<note n="0102002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0102002">依 DhP. A. III P. 521.彼犯惡業於迦葉佛時。彼名曲背 Dhāna 之意。得此惡名，亦為過去所業之果。</note>
<note n="0102003" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0102003">此於增一阿含卷二二（大正藏卷二、六六二頁上）有廣說。阿那邠邸（給孤獨）長者之女修摩提嫁後，於滿富城請佛。佛令拔取舍羅（籤籌）以決定阿羅漢之人數。時君頭波漠尚為有學，乃拔其取舍羅，立即達無學阿羅漢位。佛曰：「我弟子中第一受舍羅者君頭波漠。」A. I. P. 24。（漢譯南傳藏卷一九、三一頁）參照。</note>
<note n="0104001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0104001">A. IV, P. 354, 中阿含卷一〇（大正藏卷一、四九一頁上）據傳彌醯比丘有此事實。同為佛之侍者，舉出兩者是否混同不得而知。</note>
<note n="0105001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0105001">Pabhassara（光耀）。</note>
<note n="0106001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0106001">佛典中所現之 udayi（優陀夷）有三人。一般漢譯迦留陀夷為制定戒律因緣而出現之破戒比丘。然南傳藏則為釋迦族中一大臣之子，如本譬喻經所示：為一有德之比丘諒。諒此比丘名與傳說之間或因混雜之因由而為異傳。詳見赤沼氏《印度佛教固有名詞辭典》二六六頁參照。</note>
<note n="0106002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0106002">訂正為 addhānaṁ。</note>
<note n="0106003" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0106003">鉢頭摩為赤蓮花。優鉢羅為青蓮花（水蓮之屬）。摩利迦譯為次第花，為亞剌比亞素馨。</note>
<note n="0107004" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0107004">解為 citraṁ 之意。</note>
<note n="0108001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0108001">過去二十四佛之第十四佛。Buddhavaṁsa. P. 43; jātaka I, P. 39。</note>
<note n="0109002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0109002">訂正為 ñaṇamhi。</note>
<note n="0111001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0111001"><space quantity="0"/></note>
<note n="0111002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0111002">暹羅本讀為 Vaḍḍhakīhi，Vaḍḍhakī 乃木工之義。</note>
<note n="0112003" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0112003">讀為 sattaratana。（邏羅本）。</note>
<note n="0113001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0113001">Sahassarāja（千王）。</note>
<note n="0114001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0114001">讀為 laggetvā（暹羅本）。</note>
<note n="0114002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0114002">Sucela（美衣）。</note>
</p>
</cb:div>
